<HEADLINE> Chinese Breaks World Record in Asian Weightlifting </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGZHOU, Southeast China, (Xinhua) -- Chinese Xing Fen
shattered the women's 46kg-class clean and jerk world record by
lifting 105.5 kilograms at the Asian weightlifting championships
here on Tuesday.
</P>
