currently either under construction or at an advanced study stage
in those countries, the study said.
</P>
<P>
The Doha-based GOIC is funded by the Gulf Cooperation Council
(GCC) which groups Saudi Arabia, the United Arab Emirates (UAE),
Bahrain, Qatar, Oman and Kuwait.
</P>
<P>
The GCC states have developed an advanced petrochemical
industry to increase revenues by exporting crude oil and
exploiting large reserves of natural gas.  
