to discuss various scenarios on Austrian security policy before
the Austrian government submits a national security policy to
parliament next March, the chancellor said.
</P>
<P>
Klima is widely expected to attend NATO's summit in Madrid
which starts today and which is expected to formally announce
which eastern European countries will be invited to join the
alliance in its first wave of enlargement.
</P>
<P>
