<HEADLINE> Acting Ukrainian PM Criticizes Ministers For Inability </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Ukrainian Justice Minister Sergy
Holovaty should be condemned and Coal Industry Minister Yuri
Rusantsov should be fired due to their failure in fighting crimes,
acting Prime Minister Vasyl Durdynets said today.
</P>
<P>
