the prime minister said that he has found the grounds for the
increase of crimes -- the inability of law enforcement agencies.
</P>
<P>
In the first half of the year, a large number of criminal cases
have emerged, especially the sharp increase of economic crimes and
corruption cases, said the prime minister.
</P>
<P>
He did not reveal the details, but stressed that the
wide-spread corruption has severely damaged the reputation of the
country. 
