<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Italian rider Mario Cipollini
sprinted to defeat Germany's Erik Zabel and win the second stage
of the Tour de France on Monday.
</P>
<P>
With the win, he kept the leader's yellow jersey.
</P>
<P>
